These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: crime, drama, action, epic
1. Movie-Genre:drama is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:epic is between Movie-Genre:crime and Movie-Genre:drama##2
3. Movie-Genre:epic is on the right of Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | epic | drama | action |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Sport: cycling, water-polo, snowboarding, soccer
1. Sport:cycling is on the left of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:water-polo is in an odd position##4
3. Sport:water-polo is on the left or right of Sport:cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Sport   | water-polo | cycling | soccer | snowboarding |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
