1. Food:corn is on the left or right of Food:cabbage##3
2. Food:cabbage is in an odd position##4
3. Food:spinach is between Food:corn and Food:pepper##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Food   | cabbage | corn | spinach | pepper |

