.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Color: light-blue, white, ivory, purple
1. Color:white == Color:white##1
2. Color:purple is on the left or right of Color:ivory##3
3. Color:ivory is on the far left or far right##3
4. Color:light-blue is in an even position##4
5. Color:purple is on the left of Color:white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Color   | ivory | purple | white | light-blue |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
